<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chawlhna mun nuom lautha chawlhna,
 Ken ka na muta ie;
 Kum khawsawta pak bang lun chu,
 Zie gam hing nuom a chun,
 Lampi khat mai I nei Isu,
 Kawm I tun theihnang un.

[V2]
 Ginna'n I muh uh ka gingchai ,
 Zie gama um ding chu.

[V3]
 2. Kisazo san zie gimtheih na,
 Chu khuom bang do hitiu;
 A gingte chu pie ngei ina,
 Lallukhuk lopi chu;
 Zie muna chu Amah gingte'n ,
 A gimtheih nau cheng cheng.

[V4]
 A kengbula chun kawih tan au,
 A khawvel gimtheih nau.

[V5]
 3. Tatsate chiehna lampi chu,
 Ken ka na en zinga;
 A Pau lopi pen ma a chun,
 Lawpin a chieh zing ui,
 Zie chun keile ei na sam ui
 Lallukhuk chang dingin .

[V6]
 Lauhna cheng cheng beivek tana
 Kipahna ni achun.</lyrics>
<title>Lautha Chawlhna</title>
<hymn_number>148</hymn_number>
</song>